# ========================================
# Dependencies
# ========================================
node_modules/
# pnpm-lock.yaml is committed — matches `packageManager: pnpm@10.33.0`
# in package.json. The other lockfiles stay ignored so a teammate who
# accidentally runs `npm install` doesn't pollute the repo.
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/versions

